# apps/backend/src/modules/conversation/

## Responsibility
Manages conversation lifecycles, counts, filters, bulk edits, contact detail summaries, notes, and AI analytics.

## Design
Service layer is enriched with helper subservices for bulk edit, notes, and AI analytics. The module is built around app-scoped query filters and realtime UI sync.

## Flow
Routes list conversations, fetch counts/detail, queue bulk edits, and expose per-conversation state. Services merge customer, tag, message, pipeline, and AI summary data.

## Integration
Uses MessageService, LabelService, BusinessWebhookDispatchService, CommerceService, realtime IO, and downstream AI/flow signals.

